text: Shwikar Ibrahim () (04 May 1935 - 14 August 2020) was an Egyptian actress. She started her career in Alexandria in some tragedic roles. She was born in Alexandria. Her best known role was as Negma in the 1976 western movie Viva Zalata. Shwikar died on 14 August 2020 in Cairo, aged 81. ==References== Category:2020 deaths Category:Egyptian movie actors Category:Egyptian television actors Category:Stage actors Category:1935 births
